228
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam, ne smatram se kompetentni.

229
00:29:23,039 --> 00:29:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kratka pauza.

230
00:29:25,460 --> 00:29:29,900
